Package MedicalRecord

Class PatientMedicalRecordManager

Object
PatientMedicalRecordManager
All Implemented Interfaces:
MedicalRecordService
public class PatientMedicalRecordManager extends Object implements MedicalRecordService
The PatientMedicalRecordManager class provides functionality for patients to view and update their medical records. This class interacts with a DataProcessor to handle reading and writing operations on the medical record CSV file.

Adheres to the MedicalRecordService interface to ensure a consistent approach to managing medical records.
